The paper deals with the analysis of 3D surfaces and their geometric fine structure, which suggests a focus on computational geometry (cs.CG) and computer vision (cs.CV). The use of persistence diagrams and topological descriptors also suggests a connection to machine learning (cs.LG) and data structures (cs.DS). Finally, the evaluation of performance metrics suggests a connection to numerical analysis (cs.NA).
